(about the difference between
"up to you" and "down to you".)

851
00:51:00,040 --> 00:51:01,450
(It wasn't until later that I realized)

852
00:51:02,410 --> 00:51:04,660
(when Jiang Tian said those words,)

853
00:51:08,370 --> 00:51:09,500
(my world)

854
00:51:09,870 --> 00:51:11,370
(was already upside down.)

855
00:51:13,120 --> 00:51:14,750
(My world was turned upside down.)

856
00:51:37,930 --> 00:51:40,270
(Jiang Tian's very moment)

857
00:51:40,290 --> 00:51:41,330
Excuse me.

858
00:51:42,910 --> 00:51:44,950
Are you Jiang Tian from Class 2A?

859
00:51:44,950 --> 00:51:46,250
What can I do for you?

860
00:51:47,330 --> 00:51:49,040
My mom got burned.

861
00:51:49,040 --> 00:51:50,410
Is there something I can get for her?

862
00:51:50,950 --> 00:51:53,620
According to school rules,
that's not allowed,

863
00:51:53,620 --> 00:51:54,700
but...

864
00:51:55,250 --> 00:51:56,540
Alright. I'll get it for you.

865
00:51:56,910 --> 00:51:57,750
Thank you.

866
00:52:12,750 --> 00:52:14,750
Apply it three times a day.
Don't forget.

867
00:52:15,950 --> 00:52:17,910
By the way, your English teacher called.

868
00:52:17,910 --> 00:52:19,450
She said a student
in your class has a cold.

869
00:52:19,450 --> 00:52:20,870
Can you take the medicine to him?

870
00:52:25,330 --> 00:52:26,370
But I have something coming up.

871
00:52:27,040 --> 00:52:29,500
Well, that's okay.
I'll ask someone else to do it.

872
00:52:29,500 --> 00:52:30,770
(Health Center)

873
00:52:40,870 --> 00:52:42,250
Not going wouldn't be right, huh?

874
00:52:42,250 --> 00:52:43,100
I'll go.

875
00:52:43,100 --> 00:52:43,940
Great.

876
00:52:44,450 --> 00:52:45,450
Bye, Tian.

877
00:52:49,370 --> 00:52:51,620
You seem to get along well
with Jiang Tian.

878
00:52:51,620 --> 00:52:53,000
Why didn't you invite him?

879
00:52:53,790 --> 00:52:55,200
It's more than just getting along.

880
00:52:55,200 --> 00:52:56,580
He is my childhood sweetheart.

881
00:52:58,000 --> 00:53:00,750
(Complete cold medicine)
But Tian never attends these kinds of events.

882
00:53:00,750 --> 00:53:01,620
He's busy.

883
00:53:02,200 --> 00:53:03,080
Oh.

884
00:53:03,410 --> 00:53:05,620
But I'm surprised you asked about him.

885
00:53:06,160 --> 00:53:07,040
Why?

886
00:53:07,620 --> 00:53:10,080
I mean, from the first day
you were here,

887
00:53:10,080 --> 00:53:11,410
you two didn't get along.

888
00:53:12,290 --> 00:53:14,950
If it weren't for Jing
forcing you two together,

889
00:53:15,580 --> 00:53:17,330
you wouldn't have spoken much at all.

890
00:53:18,370 --> 00:53:20,540
I thought you weren't close,
so you didn't want him there.

891
00:53:23,160 --> 00:53:24,910
True. I'm not close to him.

892
00:53:24,910 --> 00:53:25,870
Not close at all.

893
00:53:29,660 --> 00:53:31,250
I'll be home late today.

894
00:53:32,500 --> 00:53:33,370
If my mom asks,

895
00:53:33,370 --> 00:53:35,540
just tell her the teacher needs me.

896
00:53:35,750 --> 00:53:42,220
♪Your breath turned
my world upside down♪

897
00:53:42,250 --> 00:53:44,120
You call that not close?

898
00:53:44,120 --> 00:53:45,540
He's reporting to you.

899
00:53:45,540 --> 00:53:48,040
♪Silently following behind you♪

900
00:53:48,040 --> 00:53:52,120
♪I want to be you♪

901
00:53:53,290 --> 00:53:59,290
♪What exactly is our relationship♪

902
00:54:00,040 --> 00:54:06,660
♪I want more and more of you♪

903
00:54:07,200 --> 00:54:15,200
♪I want to say out loud to the world♪

904
00:54:16,330 --> 00:54:22,250
♪You're like a shooting star
streaking across the universe♪

905
00:54:22,250 --> 00:54:26,410
♪I wave from a distance on Earth♪

906
00:54:26,410 --> 00:54:29,910
♪You grabbed me
and turned into a rainbow♪

907
00:54:29,910 --> 00:54:34,160
♪In my contacts, you're "the only one"♪

908
00:54:34,160 --> 00:54:37,700
♪Regardless of what people say♪

909
00:54:37,700 --> 00:54:46,750
♪I'll give my love to you
without reservation♪

910
00:54:47,700 --> 00:54:51,580
♪I don't know what went wrong♪

911
00:54:51,580 --> 00:54:55,000
♪I shouldn't have let you go♪

912
00:54:55,000 --> 00:55:02,330
♪I want to say out loud to the world♪

913
00:55:04,790 --> 00:55:10,660
♪You're like a shooting star
streaking across the universe♪

914
00:55:10,660 --> 00:55:14,830
♪I wave from a distance on Earth♪

915
00:55:14,830 --> 00:55:18,410
♪You grabbed me
and turned into a rainbow♪

916
00:55:18,410 --> 00:55:22,580
♪But I can only humbly
call you "the only one"♪

917
00:55:22,580 --> 00:55:26,250
♪Regardless of what people say♪

918
00:55:26,250 --> 00:55:34,870
♪They don't know about us♪

919
00:55:34,870 --> 00:55:42,160
♪Please don't let go of my hand♪

920
00:55:47,500 --> 00:55:48,790
♪I love you♪
